OL,3,CPair told they will face jail over
OL,4,C'catastrophic' care home crash
OL,6,FA stolen BMW reached speeds of 100mph
OL,7,Fbefore the driver crashed it into a
OL,8,Fcare home in a "catastrophic impact",
OL,9,Fa court heard.
OL,11,FA 94-year-old resident suffered
OL,12,Ffractured vertebrae and other elderly
OL,13,Fpeople living at Highcliffe Care Home
OL,14,Fin Sunderland were injured when the
OL,15,Fcar slammed into the exterior wall
OL,16,Fcausing the ceiling to collapse.
