OL,3,CPair told they will face jail over
OL,4,C'catastrophic' care home crash
OL,6,FSam Asgari-Tabar, 21, was behind the
OL,7,Fwheel of the BMW 3-Series which he had
OL,8,Fstolen along with Reece Parish earlier
OL,9,Fin the evening of 10 July in Fenham,
OL,10,FNewcastle.
OL,12,FProsecutors said the pair went to
OL,13,Fcheck out the car which was advertised
OL,14,Ffor sale on Facebook before they drove
OL,15,Foff with a terrified woman who was
OL,16,Fselling it on behalf of a relative
OL,17,Fstill in it.
OL,19,FThey eventually managed to remove her
OL,20,Fbefore speeding off again.
