OL,3,CPair told they will face jail over
OL,4,C'catastrophic' care home crash
OL,6,FPolice began to follow the pair and
OL,7,Fthe video shown at Newcastle Crown
OL,8,FCourt showed the pursuing officers
OL,9,Freaching 100mph on residential streets
OL,10,Fin Sunderland to keep up.
OL,12,FParish, of Fordham Road, Sunderland,
OL,13,Fand Asgari-Tabar, of no fixed abode,
OL,14,Fappeared at court via a videolink
OL,15,Fhaving previously admitted robbery.
OL,17,FAsgari-Tabar was behind the wheel when
OL,18,Fit crashed into the care home `
OL,19,Falthough Parish had been driving
OL,20,Fearlier ` and he admitted causing
OL,21,Fserious injury by dangerous driving.
