OL,3,CPair told they will face jail over
OL,4,C'catastrophic' care home crash
OL,6,FThe 94-year-old victim had previously
OL,7,Fenjoyed activities at the care home
OL,8,Fbut since suffering the serious
OL,9,Finjury, which kept her in hospital for
OL,10,Fmonths, she has lost her enthusiasm
OL,11,Fand she has to wear a brace, the court
OL,12,Fheard.
OL,14,FEmma Dowling, prosecuting, said: "The
OL,15,Fcare home was subject to what is
OL,16,Fdescribed as a catastrophic impact by
OL,17,Fthe car."
