OL,3,CPair told they will face jail over
OL,4,C'catastrophic' care home crash
OL,6,FBody-worn camera footage showed the
OL,7,Fscene as officers entered the wrecked
OL,8,Fbuilding to try to rescue injured
OL,9,Fresidents.
OL,11,FCCTV from the building showed Parish
OL,12,Fflee the scene but Asgari-Tabar was
OL,13,Farrested by the car.
OL,15,FThe care home, which can accommodate
OL,16,Fpeople with dementia, had to be
OL,17,Fevacuated.
OL,19,FIt suffered damage costing #260,000
OL,20,Fand the loss of capacity cost the
OL,21,Fowners #411,000, the court heard.
