OL,3,CPair told they will face jail over
OL,4,C'catastrophic' care home crash
OL,6,FNicholas Lane, representing him, told
OL,7,Fthe court: "He is deeply ashamed of
OL,8,Fhis behaviour."
OL,10,FChristopher Knox, representing Parish,
OL,11,Freminded the judge of his client's
OL,12,Fyouth.
OL,14,FJudge Stephen Earl will sentence the
OL,15,Fpair on 11 November and warned they
OL,16,Fface "substantial" custodial sentences.
OL,18,FTwo elderly residents died following
OL,19,Fthe crash but their deaths do not form
OL,20,Fpart of the prosecution case.
